      "content": "I have gathered the time\u2011zones, current workload, and existing events for the next week. Based on the data, I generated three candidate 1\u2011hour windows on Tuesdays that are free for all participants:\n1. 2025\u201112\u201110 14:00\u201115:00\u202fUTC\n2. 2025\u201112\u201117 13:00\u201114:00\u202fUTC\n3. 2025\u201112\u201124 15:00\u201116:00\u202fUTC\nI will now evaluate these slots with the **balanced** priority so that the presenter\u2019s workload stays as even as possible across the 8 weeks.",
